  "detailed_description": "Cyberkiller 2049 is a platform-action fast-paced game that battles numerous enemies on destructible platforms. Manipulate the character, kill with one hit, sprint, kill enemies. Picking up bats, remote-controlled bombs. Fight enemies with different abilities.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction of the boss</h2>There are three bosses designed in the game, namely Hammer, Predator and Experimental. Cyberkiller 2049 hopes to bring wonderful boss battles to players<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/d941b5cde4386cb7846ba175e03146c0.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction of the enemy</h2>Cyberkiller 2049 has dozens of enemies with different mechanics, which, along with the game's destructible walls, form the core gameplay of the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Punk boy:</h2> Simple enemies but not to be taken lightly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/24456d7f8383c15232b1c074bbb15c12.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gang boy:</h2>Can throw a bat and pick up a bat, dealing knock down damage to the player, close range melee attack .<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/01e683ca58e73da66b99af1398bd2035.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bomb boy:</h2>Throw a bomb, which explodes after a brief delay dealing range damage, close range melee attacks .<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/c9676016c4c2e4bab18f6bc6ec9d50ce.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rugby boy:</h2>Players can be found through walls, and can destroy walls in the path.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.poster.avif?t=1730379533\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.webm?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047340/extras/2e5f9de4a29a74587cc0caadb505c1b8.mp4?t=1730379533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
